'''六氟合钒(III)酸铵'''是一种[[配位化合物|配位化合物]]，化学式为(NH<sub>4</sub>)<sub>3</sub>[VF<sub>6</sub>]。

==制备及性质==
将[[氟化氢铵|氟化氢铵]]、[[三氧化二钒|三氧化二钒]]和[[硫代硫酸铵|硫代硫酸铵]]置于水中，加入少量[[氢氟酸|氢氟酸]]，于180 °C进行水热反应，可以得到(NH<sub>4</sub>)<sub>3</sub>VF<sub>6</sub>晶体。<ref name=He>He, Li-jie; Zhang, Dong; Feng, Shou-hua; Chen, Gang; Zou, Bo. Hydrothermal synthesis, structure characterization and magnetic studies of perovskite-​type fluorides K<sub>2</sub>NaVF<sub>6</sub> and (NH<sub>4</sub>)​3VF<sub>6</sub>. ''Chemical Research in Chinese Universities'', 2012. 28 (3): 371-374. ISSN: 1005-9040.</ref>[[三氧化二钒|三氧化二钒]]和[[氟化氢铵|氟化氢铵]]直接反应也能得到(NH<sub>4</sub>)<sub>3</sub>VF<sub>6</sub>。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Synthesis and Reactivity in Inorganic and Metal-Organic Chemistry|volume=21|issue=5|language=en|issn=0094-5714|date=1991-05|pages=779–791|doi=10.1080/15533179108016842|url=http://www.tandfonline.com/doi/abs/10.1080/15533179108016842|title=Fluorination of Vanadium Oxides|accessdate=2021-01-11|author=B. N. Wani, U. R. K. Rao}}</ref>

它可以被[[二氟化氙|二氟化氙]]氧化为(NH<sub>4</sub>)<sub>3</sub>VF<sub>8</sub>。<ref>Slivnik, Joze; Druzina, Branke; Zemva, Boris. Reactions of some ammonium fluorometalates with xenon difluoride. ''Zeitschrift fuer Naturforschung, Teil B:  Anorganische Chemie, Organische Chemie'', 1981. 36B (11): 1457-1460. ISSN: 0340-5087.</ref>它在250~450 °C分解，经(NH<sub>4</sub>)<sub>2</sub>VF<sub>5</sub>、NH<sub>4</sub>VF<sub>4</sub>，最终得到[[三氟化钒|三氟化钒]]。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Transactions of the Japan Institute of Metals|volume=17|issue=5|language=en|issn=0021-4434|date=1976|pages=287–293|doi=10.2320/matertrans1960.17.287|url=https://www.jstage.jst.go.jp/article/matertrans1960/17/5/17_5_287/_article|title=Thermal Decomposition of Ammonium Hexafluorovanadate (III)|accessdate=2021-01-11|author=K\={o}ichir\={o} K\={o}yama, Yasuhiko Hashimoto}}</ref>

